<plot>Angel is a fisherman from Mazatlan, who moves with his family to Mexico City in search of better life. In Mexico City they become neighbors of Eva and Miguel. Eva is a very unhappy woman who lives tortured by her husband and daughter. Miguel, her invalid husband, pretends to be a good person, but he is a pure evil. Years ago he raped a woman and Eva not only pardoned him but even adopted a girl and raised her like her own. Miguel blames Eva for his accident and has poisoned his daughter Delia against her. Delia adores her father and hates Eva. In addition, Miguel only pretends to be invalid. Eva, frustrated as a wife, mother and woman will find passion in the arms of Angel.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?529664</url></doc>
